Available Tools: get_temperature | get_humidity | get_wind_speed | get_uv_index
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "unit": "celsius|fahrenheit" }
Response Schema: { "value": number, "unit": "string", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: What is the current humidity in Austin?
Call: { "func_call": "get_humidity", "location": "Austin", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 71, "unit": "%", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T15:00:00Z" }

Question: Check the wind speed in Boston right now.
Call: { "func_call": "get_wind_speed", "location": "Boston", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 22.4, "unit": "km/h", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T15:00:00Z" }

